      • getTables

        protected List<String> getTables()
        Get the database table names to be cleared (in inverse order of creation).

        Each string will used to drop the tables if exists passing an SQL statement to SQLiteDatabase.execSQL(String sql) to be executed.

        Specified by:
        getTables in class AbstractDBHelper
        Returns:
        an ordered list of strings containing the database table names to be cleared.
